title: The Dumbest Attempts To Cancel MrBeast

media:group.media:title: The Dumbest Attempts To Cancel MrBeast
media:group.media:description:
People have tried to cancel MrBeast many times. The reasons for which vary, but with so many cancellation attempts over such a long period of time, some of them are bound to be a lot pettier than others. This video will cover three of those incredibly stupid attempts, from people being angry at Chris and MrBeast for dressing up as a helicopter, to That Vegan Teacher claiming that MrBeast was destroying the environment by not having pineapple on his "Worlds largest slice of pizza".

These are, The Dumbest Attempts To Cancel MrBeast.
